tourBios.otherInfo: Rookie on the 2000 BUY.COM TOUR...no prior experience on the PGA TOUR...has played in only four BUY.COM TOUR events making the cut just once in the 1998 Tri-Cities Open...finished tied for 57th...NCAA Academic All-American 1992-94...father began to teach him the game of golf at the age of three.

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the Web.com Tour was T12th in 2000 at the BUY.COM Upstate Classic.
